## Project Structure

```
hq/
├── docker-compose.yml          # Dev environment orchestration
├── docker/
│   ├── Dockerfile              # Multi-stage: api-dev, api-builder, ui-dev, ui-builder, prod
│   └── bin/                    # Init scripts (init-dev with hot-reload, init, init-debug, init-test)
├── go/                         # Go backend (module: nathejk.dk, Go 1.23)
│   ├── cmd/api/                # Single HTTP API service (main, routes, handlers)
│   │   └── app/                # Shared JSON API helpers (errors, middleware, server)
│   ├── internal/
│   │   ├── data/               # Read models: team, member, signup, users, tokens, permissions
│   │   ├── payment/mobilepay/  # MobilePay/Vipps ePayment REST client
│   │   ├── sms/                # CPSMS SMS gateway client
│   │   └── mailer/             # SMTP mailer
│   ├── nathejk/
│   │   ├── commands/           # Write-side command handlers (team, lok, checkgroup)
│   │   └── table/              # Event-sourced read projections (one per aggregate)
│   │       ├── year/, klan/, patrulje/, senior/, spejder/
│   │       ├── signup/, checkgroup/, checkpoint/, checkpersonnel/
│   │       ├── scan/, lok/, payment/, personnel/, patruljemerged/
│   │       └── (each: table.go, consumer.go, query.go, commands.go, table.sql, filter.go)
│   ├── pkg/
│   │   ├── sqlpersister/       # Generic SQL executor (write-side adapter)
│   │   └── tablerow/           # Interfaces: SQLTableRow, Consumer, EntityChangedPublisher
│   └── superfluids/
│       ├── streaminterface/    # Core pub/sub abstractions (Stream, Publisher, Subscriber, Consumer, Message)
│       ├── jetstream/          # NATS JetStream implementation of streaminterface
│       └── xstream/            # Stream multiplexer (Mux) — routes messages to consumers
├── vue/                        # Vue 3 frontend (TypeScript, Vite 6, PrimeVue 4, Tailwind CSS 3)
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── views/              # Page-level components (Home, Year, Klan, Patrulje, Post, Mail, Kort, etc.)
│   │   ├── components/         # Reusable UI components (Navigation, Footer, DayTimePicker, etc.)
│   │   ├── composables/        # Shared reactive state (globalstate.ts, datefilters.ts, useBuildInfo.ts)
│   │   ├── plugins/            # Axios (HTTP client), mitt (event bus), Sentry
│   │   ├── router/             # Vue Router (HTML5 history mode, lazy-loaded routes)
│   │   └── stores/             # Pinia (installed, minimally used — state mostly in composables/local refs)
│   ├── vite.config.ts          # Dev proxy: /api → http://api (Docker service)
│   └── tailwind.config.js
└── .github/workflows/          # CI/CD: build-and-publish to DockerHub (nathejk/hq)
```

---

## Technology Stack

### Backend (Go)
- **Language**: Go 1.23
- **Module**: `nathejk.dk`
- **HTTP Router**: `julienschmidt/httprouter`
- **Database**: MariaDB 10.8 via `go-sql-driver/mysql`
- **Query Builder**: `doug-martin/goqu/v9`
- **Event Streaming**: NATS JetStream (`nats-io/nats.go`)
- **Shared Domain Types**: `github.com/nathejk/shared-go/types` (TeamID, MemberID, UserID, etc.)
- **Excel Export**: `xuri/excelize/v2`
- **Email**: `wneessen/go-mail` (SMTP)
- **SMS**: CPSMS REST API (`api.cpsms.dk`)
- **Payments**: MobilePay/Vipps ePayment REST API

### Frontend (Vue)
- **Framework**: Vue 3 with `<script setup>` (Composition API)
- **Language**: TypeScript ~5.4 (mixed — some views use plain JS setup)
- **Build Tool**: Vite 6.3
- **UI Library**: PrimeVue 4 (Aura theme) with auto-import via `unplugin-vue-components`
- **CSS**: Tailwind CSS 3.4
- **HTTP Client**: Axios (baseURL: `/api/`, adds `X-YearSlug` header)
- **Map**: Leaflet 1.9
- **Drag & Drop**: vuedraggable 4.1
- **Rich Text**: Quill 2.0
- **Icons**: FontAwesome (solid, brands, regular) + PrimeIcons
- **State**: Composables with module-level `ref()` (singleton pattern), Pinia available but barely used
- **Routing**: vue-router 4 (HTML5 history, lazy-loaded routes)

### Infrastructure
- **Containerization**: Docker with multi-stage Dockerfile
- **Orchestration**: Docker Compose (dev), Traefik (routing)
- **Database**: MariaDB 10.8 (timezone: Europe/Copenhagen)
- **Event Bus**: NATS JetStream (external Docker network)
- **Reverse Proxy**: Traefik (external) + `jrgensen/gateway` (internal subdomain routing)
- **CI/CD**: GitHub Actions → DockerHub (`nathejk/hq`)
- **Auth**: External service at `lukmigind.nathejk.dk` (JWT cookie-based)

---

## Domain Model

### Core Entities
- **Year** — An event edition (slug, headline, description, cities, dates)
- **Patrulje** (Patrol) — A team of scouts (spejdere). Has name, group, korps, liga, contact info, members, team number, signup status
- **Klan** (Clan) — A team of seniors. Has name, group, korps, members, signup status, lok assignment, payment tracking
- **Spejder** (Scout) — Individual patrol member (name, address, contact, birthday, T-shirt size)
- **Senior** — Individual clan member (name, address, contact, birthday, diet, T-shirt size)
- **Checkgroup** — A group of checkpoints with timing schemes (fixed, relative, none), mandatory flag
- **Checkpoint** — Individual checkpoint within a checkgroup (location, time windows, sort order)
- **Checkpersonnel** — Volunteers staffing checkpoints with time shifts
- **Scan** — QR code scan events (team scanned at checkpoint)
- **Lok** — Physical camp locations that klans are assigned to
- **Signup** — Registration record tracking email/phone verification and pincode
- **Payment** — Payment lifecycle: requested → reserved → received (MobilePay)
- **Personnel** — Event volunteers/staff (gøglere/badutter)

### Shared Types (from `nathejk/shared-go`)
`TeamID`, `MemberID`, `UserID`, `LokID`, `CheckgroupID`, `CheckpointID`, `YearSlug`, `TeamType` (patrulje/klan), `SignupStatus`, `PhoneNumber`, `EmailAddress`, `Date`

---

## API Endpoints

| Method | Path | Purpose |
|--------|------|---------|
| GET | `/api/home` | Dashboard stats |
| GET/POST/PATCH/DELETE | `/api/year/:slug` | Year CRUD |
| GET/POST/PUT/DELETE | `/api/checkgroup(s)` | Checkgroup management |
| POST/PUT/DELETE | `/api/checkpersonnel` | Checkpoint personnel |
| GET | `/api/personnel` | List all personnel |
| POST | `/api/signup` | Team signup (creates team + sends verification email) |
| POST | `/api/signup/pincode` | PIN code verification |
| GET/PUT | `/api/patrulje/:id` | Patrol CRUD |
| PUT | `/api/patrulje/:id/start` | Start a patrol |
| GET/PUT/PATCH | `/api/klan/:id` | Clan CRUD |
| GET/PUT/DELETE | `/api/lok/:id` | Lok (camp location) management |
| GET | `/api/badut` | Performer list |
| GET | `/api/excel/klan`, `/api/excel/patrulje`, `/api/excel/personnel` | Excel exports |
| GET | `/api/mail/recipients` | Mail recipient list |
| POST | `/api/mail/send` | Send mail |
| GET | `/api/v1/healthcheck` | Health check |

---

## Development Setup

### Prerequisites
- Docker and Docker Compose
- External Docker networks: `traefik`, `jetstream` (must exist before starting)
- A running NATS JetStream instance on the `jetstream` network
- A running Traefik instance on the `traefik` network (or access via `hq.local.nathejk.dk`)

### Starting Dev Environment
```
docker compose up
```

### Services & URLs
| Service | Internal URL | External URL |
|---------|-------------|--------------|
| Frontend (Vite dev) | `http://ui:80` | `http://hq.local.nathejk.dk` |
| API | `http://api:80` | `http://hq.local.nathejk.dk/api/` |
| DB Admin (Adminer) | `http://adminer:8080` | `http://mysql.hq.local.nathejk.dk` |
| MariaDB | `mysql:3306` | — |

### Dev Workflow
- **Go API**: Hot-reload via `inotifywait` — automatically rebuilds and restarts on file changes in `./go`
- **Vue Frontend**: Vite HMR — changes in `./vue/src` are reflected instantly
- **Database**: MariaDB tables auto-created on startup via `CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS` in each table consumer
- **Events**: Read models rebuilt from JetStream on each API restart (event replay)

### Environment Variables (dev defaults)
| Variable | Value |
|----------|-------|
| `JETSTREAM_DSN` | `nats://jetstream:4222` |
| `DB_DSN` | `root:ib@tcp(mysql:3306)/hq?parseTime=true` |
| `SMS_DSN` | `cpsms://TOKEN@api.cpsms.dk` |
| `AUTH_BASEURL` | `https://lukmigind.nathejk.dk` |

### Frontend Dev Proxy
Vite proxies `/api/*` to `http://api` (the Go service inside Docker).

---

## Coding Conventions

### Go
- Single service binary at `cmd/api/`
- Each table projection follows a consistent structure: `table.go`, `consumer.go`, `query.go`, `commands.go`, `table.sql`, `filter.go`
- SQL schemas embedded via `//go:embed table.sql`
- Domain events carry `eventId`, `correlationId`, `causationId` for tracing
- Commands perform dirty-checking against read model before publishing events
- Use `goqu` query builder for newer modules; raw SQL for older ones
- MySQL-specific SQL: `INSERT ... ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE`, `IF()`, `?` placeholders

### Vue / TypeScript
- Use `<script setup>` (Composition API) for all components
- PrimeVue components are auto-imported (no manual imports needed)
- State management: prefer composables with module-level `ref()` for shared state; use local `ref()` per view for component data
- API calls via `http.get/post/put/patch/delete` from `src/plugins/axios`
- Lazy-load all routes except HomeView
- Danish locale for date formatting (`da-DK`)
- Tailwind CSS for styling; PrimeVue Aura theme for components

### Language
- The domain uses Danish terminology: patrulje (patrol), klan (clan), spejder (scout), senior, gøgler/badut (performer), lok (camp location), post (checkpoint), postlinje (checkpoint line), postmandskab (checkpoint personnel), kort (map), år/year (year edition)
- UI text and labels are in Danish
- Code (variables, functions, comments) is in English, but domain entity names retain Danish forms

---

## CI/CD

- **Trigger**: Push to `main` or pull request
- **Pipeline**: GitHub Actions → Docker multi-stage build → Push to DockerHub (`nathejk/hq`)
- **Tagging**: `latest` (main only) + `{branch}.{run_number}`
- **Build args injected**: `GIT_COMMIT`, `GIT_BRANCH`, `BUILD_NUMBER`, `BUILD_VERSION`
- **Production image**: Minimal Alpine with compiled Go binary + built Vue static files, single port 80

---

## External Integrations

| Service | Purpose | Config |
|---------|---------|--------|
| NATS JetStream | Event streaming (CQRS event bus) | `JETSTREAM_DSN` |
| MobilePay/Vipps | Payment processing | `PAYMENT_DSN` |
| CPSMS | SMS gateway (Danish provider) | `SMS_DSN` |
| SMTP | Email (verification, notifications) | `SMTP_HOST`, `SMTP_PORT`, etc. |
| `lukmigind.nathejk.dk` | Authentication service (JWT) | `AUTH_BASEURL` |